{
  "texts": [
    "Sequences with predicted signal peptides were truncated at the predicted signal peptide cleavage site.",
    "Two bacterial FeSOD proteins, both lacking a predicted signal peptide, and the previously characterized 63 E. coli FeSOD (as a positive control) were also assayed.",
    "The selected sequences had between 80% and 90% identity to the closest training set sequence and diverse scores on the ESM-1v and ESM-MSA metrics.",
    "Sequences were also filtered by manual inspection to remove those with large insertions or deletions compared to the closest reference sequences or long repeats, and a methionine was added to the start of a few of the sequences.",
    "Sequences were selected on the basis of a series of filters."
  ]
}